      "I start shaking uncontrollably in shock. I look to my doula who safeguarded my birth like a true birth keeper woman. She reassures me we can do this, calmly and lovingly.",
      "My husband goes to speak to the midwife privately and tells me he told her 'my wife does not want a C-section. If there is no true medical emergency for this, why is she being pressured into it? What can you do to help her have the natural birth?'",
