      "The adjustment was hard for his brother. I was quite neurotic about him coming close to his new born brother when he was sick.",
      "We had made the mistake of starting school with my first child and he was catching every single bug and bringing it home to his brother. In retrospect I wish I just let him be home with both of us and we could have all cocooned together. But part of me also just wanted me and my newborn to get to know one another.",
